Description: <insert up to 60 chars description> (Python 3)
 This is Group Guess. It intends to be a simple, yet extensible Family Feud
 clone. It features the ability to store games in JSON files.
 .
 This package installs the library for Python 3.
 .
 It also installs gg-gamesave, used to open JSON-format gamesaves.

